line-width.description: The length of the connection line takes effect only when the value of the text-position property of the timeline component is true, and the space property is invalid after it is set
line-width.description_zh: 连接线长度，仅当 timeline 组件 text-position 属性取值为 true 时生效，设置后 space 属性失效

space.description: Node width, the value can be a number, a numeric string with a length unit, and a percentage string, and the number will be px as the length unit by default
space.description_zh: 节点宽度， 取值为数字、带长度单位的数值字符串和百分比字符串，数字会默认以px为长度单位

typeDetail.ITimelineItem:
interface ITimelineItem {
  name: string // 节点名称
  activeColor: 'success' | 'warning' | 'error' | Component
  time?: string // 节点时间
  error?: boolean // 是否异常状态
  disabled?: boolean // 是否禁用
  type?: ITimelineItemType // 节点类型
}
